When you are ready to make medicine a permenant process:
$ crontab -e

Insert line 1 at the bottom. Save file and exit. Use:
$ crontab -l 
To verify your cronjob has been established

Note:
	In the final deployment, move the raspberry-pi directory somewhere outside the webserver (such as /home/pi).
	These files contain the username and password to the database. These files can be read from a web browser.
